修改项目配置       |  ✅   |  ❌  |   ❌
用户管理           |  ✅   |  ❌  |   ❌
系统设置           |  ✅   |  ❌  |   ❌
```

**路由保护示例:**
```typescript
// routes/index.ts
import { authenticateToken, requireRole } from '../auth/middleware';

// 公开路由(不需要认证)
fastify.get('/health', async (request, reply) => { ... });

// 需要认证的路由
fastify.get('/iterations', { 
  preHandler: [authenticateToken] 
}, async (request, reply) => { ... });

// 需要 Admin 角色的路由
fastify.delete('/iterations/:id', { 
  preHandler: [authenticateToken, requireRole('admin')] 
}, async (request, reply) => { ... });

// 允许 Admin 和 User 的路由
fastify.post('/projects/:id/activate', { 
  preHandler: [authenticateToken, requireRole('admin', 'user')] 
}, async (request, reply) => { ... });
```

